abstract: After steadily rising in popularity over the last several weeks, former New York City Mayor Michael Bloomberg appears to have surpassed U.S. Senator Elizabeth Warren among registered voters for the 2020 Democratic nomination, according to a Reuters/Ipsos national public opinion poll released on Thursday.
snippet: After steadily rising in popularity over the last several weeks, former New York City Mayor Michael Bloomberg appears to have surpassed U.S. Senator Elizabeth Warren among registered voters for the 2020 Democratic nomination, according to a Reuter...
lead_paragraph: NEW YORK — After steadily rising in popularity over the last several weeks, former New York City Mayor Michael Bloomberg appears to have surpassed U.S. Senator Elizabeth Warren among registered voters for the 2020 Democratic nomination, according to a Reuters/Ipsos national public opinion poll released on Thursday.
headline_main: Movin' on Up: Bloomberg Glides Past Warren to No. 3 in Democratic Race-Reuters/Ipsos Poll
headline_print_headline: Movin' on Up: Bloomberg Glides Past Warren to No. 3 in Democratic Race-Reuters/Ipsos Poll

abstract: The U.S. Senate is holding an impeachment trial on charges by the House of Representatives that President Donald Trump abused his powers and obstructed a congressional inquiry into whether he put pressure on Ukraine to investigate Democratic presidential contender Joe Biden.
snippet: The U.S. Senate is holding an impeachment trial on charges by the House of Representatives that President Donald Trump abused his powers and obstructed a congressional inquiry into whether he put pressure on Ukraine to investigate Democratic presi...
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - The U.S. Senate is holding an impeachment trial on charges by the House of Representatives that President Donald Trump abused his powers and obstructed a congressional inquiry into whether he put pressure on Ukraine to investigate Democratic presidential contender Joe Biden.
headline_main: Republican Senators to Watch in Battle Over Trump Impeachment Trial Witnesses
headline_print_headline: Republican Senators to Watch in Battle Over Trump Impeachment Trial Witnesses

abstract: The Hawkeye State gets a lot of flak for its first-in-the-nation caucuses, but its conception of democracy has staying power.
snippet: The Hawkeye State gets a lot of flak for its first-in-the-nation caucuses, but its conception of democracy has staying power.
lead_paragraph: And now, all eyes turn to Iowa.
